Package io.github.jnodorp.jiffybox.models

Klasse Disk

java.lang.Object
io.github.jnodorp.jiffybox.models.Disk
public class Disk extends Object
A disk consists of a name, a filesystem, a size (in MB), a creation timestamp, a status and a distribution.
